## Data Source & Structure {.smaller}

::: columns
::: {.column width="50%"}
**American Community Survey (ACS)**

- **Source**: U.S. Census Bureau
- **Type**: 5-Year Estimates (2018–2022 and 2019–2023)
- **Coverage**: All 50 states + DC
- **Granularity**: County-level (FIPS codes)
- **Sample**: Rolling surveys pooled over 5 years

**Records analyzed:**

- 2022: `r nrow(water_2022_clean)` counties
- 2023: `r nrow(water_2023_clean)` counties
- Matched year-over-year: `r nrow(water_change)` counties
:::

::: {.column width="50%"}
**Variables in the Dataset**

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `geoid` | County FIPS code (identifier) |
| `name` | County + State name |
| `total_pop` | Total county population |
| `plumbing` | # HH lacking plumbing |
| `percent_lacking_plumbing` | % HH lacking plumbing |

> *"Complete plumbing" = hot/cold water + flush toilet + bathtub/shower*
:::
:::

