## Data Cleaning {.smaller}

::: columns
::: {.column width="45%"}
**Steps applied identically to both years:**

- Remove counties with missing or zero `total_pop`
- Exclude all non-state U.S. territories (5 entities)
- Convert `percent_lacking_plumbing` → proportion `rate` (0–1)

> Wrapping all logic inside `clean_water()` follows the **DRY principle** —
> a single definition propagates consistently to both the 2022 and 2023 datasets,
> eliminating any risk of year-specific inconsistencies downstream.
:::
